1
00:00:00,670 --> 00:00:01,490
Yebin.

2
00:00:02,280 --> 00:00:03,450
Think carefully.

3
00:00:04,200 --> 00:00:06,000
It's all stated in the contract.

4
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:16,050
Very good.

5
00:00:17,590 --> 00:00:18,250
Keep going.

6
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:22,440
Put on lipstick for her gently.

7
00:00:31,790 --> 00:00:33,250
I'll add a bit more for you.

8
00:00:36,290 --> 00:00:37,700
Our lips are matching.

9
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:51,370
[Morning,
in Lee Sumin's office]

10
00:00:56,370 --> 00:01:00,180
[Ratings trend of Wonder-X's reality show]

11
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:04,709
Everyone is here, yeah?

12
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:07,510
I'm not one to beat around the bush.

13
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:13,420
Let's look at the data
of your last reality show.

14
00:01:17,250 --> 00:01:21,650
The number of views, trending topics,
interactions, and Return on Investment

15
00:01:21,990 --> 00:01:24,310
are all below expectations.

16
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:26,900
Way below expectations.

17
00:01:29,740 --> 00:01:32,170
Because the agency values you

18
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:36,060
they've gathered connections,
capital, and time to invest in you.

19
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:39,340
But the data and reception are poor.

20
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:41,340
This is the harsh reality.

21
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:44,400
If you aren't consistently profitable,

22
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:47,030
you'll soon be replaced by other rookies.

23
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:52,160
So we need to adjust our strategy.

24
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:55,770
We need a more direct and intense approach
to create buzz.

25
00:01:55,770 --> 00:01:58,590
That is, livestreaming.

26
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:02,180
It's not just a livestream
but a live commerce.

27
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:06,060
The agency has signed a promotion contract
for a lipstick series.

28
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:07,630
This is your chance.

29
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,410
What you need to do

30
00:02:09,410 --> 00:02:11,950
is to highlight the product well,

31
00:02:11,950 --> 00:02:13,480
promote sales,

32
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,460
and showcase your teamwork

33
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:17,700
to return to the spotlight.

34
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,600
What are the livestream
format and procedure?

35
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:31,260
The planning team is
still fine-tuning the details.

36
00:02:31,260 --> 00:02:33,810
The key points are product experience,

37
00:02:33,810 --> 00:02:35,250
interactive sales,

38
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:36,850
and the chemistry of you two.

39
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:40,460
In particular, you have to be natural

40
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,200
and show chemistry.

41
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:44,329
This is what the viewers and fans want.

42
00:02:45,210 --> 00:02:46,329
You were too rigid

43
00:02:47,420 --> 00:02:48,630
in the last reality show.

44
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:50,370
Of course no one would watch it.

45
00:02:50,370 --> 00:02:51,300
Don't you agree?

46
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,240
But

47
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:58,750
we don't have
any livestreaming experience at all,

48
00:02:59,710 --> 00:03:01,660
not to mention live commerce.

49
00:03:02,820 --> 00:03:04,120
Then learn.

50
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:06,340
The agency will provide training;

51
00:03:06,730 --> 00:03:09,800
how to frame yourself in the camera,
the script, and product knowledge.

52
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,700
The key is your attitude.

53
00:03:11,990 --> 00:03:13,560
I understand

54
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:16,690
about your artistic pursuit.

55
00:03:17,450 --> 00:03:19,440
But you have to remember this:

56
00:03:20,290 --> 00:03:21,620
if you don't make money,

57
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:25,280
practice studios and platforms
won't be available to you.

58
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:28,210
The agency will give you
opportunities and resources,

59
00:03:28,210 --> 00:03:30,810
which you need to use to create value.

60
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:37,810
The contract, live script,
and training schedule

61
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:39,340
will be relayed to you soon.

62
00:03:39,550 --> 00:03:40,860
For the next week,

63
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:43,540
cancel all other irrelevant work.

64
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:45,690
Focus on the livestream prep.

65
00:03:47,570 --> 00:03:49,540
Remember, this livestream

66
00:03:49,950 --> 00:03:52,350
is not simply a promotion.

67
00:03:52,850 --> 00:03:54,740
You need to show the agency

68
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:57,360
why your group is worth investing in

69
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,000
and worth the risk.

70
00:04:02,090 --> 00:04:03,380
Yes, Mr. Lee.

71
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:07,110
Yes, understood.

72
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:07,700
Yes.

73
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,650
Good.

74
00:04:10,410 --> 00:04:11,610
That's all for today.

75
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,490
Ji-eun, stay behind.

76
00:04:13,490 --> 00:04:15,020
I have something to ask you.

77
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:20,279
Go back first.

78
00:04:21,930 --> 00:04:23,110
Thank you.

79
00:04:24,290 --> 00:04:25,330
Thank you.

80
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,560
If you want to debut,

81
00:04:44,010 --> 00:04:46,140
you have to do well in this livestream.

82
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,810
Make sure you're in prime condition.

83
00:04:50,909 --> 00:04:51,640
Yes, Mr. Lee.

84
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,550
I'll do my best.

85
00:04:56,170 --> 00:04:56,770
Oh, right.

86
00:04:57,420 --> 00:04:59,020
And about Yebin,

87
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:01,580
she seems more unstable than I thought.

88
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:04,250
You've been with her for the longest time.

89
00:05:04,910 --> 00:05:06,270
Take care of her.

90
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:09,640
Tell me if you need help.

91
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:13,980
I hope this livestream will be a success.

92
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:18,190
I'll talk to the leader.

93
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:20,970
Good.

94
00:05:22,770 --> 00:05:23,440
Go along.

95
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:45,580
Attention, everyone.

96
00:05:46,090 --> 00:05:48,710
The livestream of Wonder-X will begin now.

97
00:05:49,130 --> 00:05:49,930
Are you ready?

98
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:52,140
OK.

99
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:56,840
Three, two, one, action.

100
00:06:01,340 --> 00:06:02,370
Hello, everyone.

101
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:04,510
I'm the host today again.

102
00:06:04,610 --> 00:06:06,670
Our goal is to get 15 million viewers.

103
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:09,450
We prepared something fun today too.

104
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:14,600
Yebin-unnie, what are you doing?

105
00:06:14,770 --> 00:06:15,750
Come sit down.

106
00:06:18,740 --> 00:06:21,620
I'll teach you how to
say "lipstick" in Chinese.

107
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:23,000
Follow me.

108
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,710
"Kou hong."

109
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:30,370
"Kou hong"...

110
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,080
Unnie.

111
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:36,110
You sound so awkward!

112
00:06:37,490 --> 00:06:38,870
Shut up.

113
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:41,930
Ji-eun, it's your turn.

114
00:06:42,650 --> 00:06:43,490
You can do it.

115
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:50,110
"Kou hong piao liang."
[T/N: "Pretty lipstick" in Chinese]

116
00:06:50,290 --> 00:06:51,480
Ji-eun!

117
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,659
Isn't she so gentle?

118
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:56,390
She has such versatile charm.

119
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:27,920
[Simulation of the couple livestream]

120
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:35,050
Yebin, don't look so tense.

121
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:35,810
OK?

122
00:07:37,340 --> 00:07:38,970
Make your gaze gentler.

123
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,180
Show more of your charm.

124
00:07:43,130 --> 00:07:44,520
Relax a bit more.

125
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,260
OK.

126
00:07:48,330 --> 00:07:49,400
By the way,

127
00:07:50,530 --> 00:07:53,060
why are your faces so red?

128
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:01,090
Yebin-unnie was staring at you
for so long.

129
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:07,280
Ji-eun, stop looking.

130
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,800
The live's starting.

131
00:08:33,780 --> 00:08:35,130
OK. Good.

132
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,679
Yebin, keep this expression.

133
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,400
OK?

134
00:08:43,650 --> 00:08:46,550
Ji-eun, make your gaze gentler as usual.

135
00:08:47,770 --> 00:08:49,120
OK, OK, OK, OK!

136
00:08:49,310 --> 00:08:49,970
Let's do it.

137
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,900
Maintain that.

138
00:08:52,230 --> 00:08:52,890
Good.

139
00:08:52,890 --> 00:08:53,890
Ji-eun, that's great.

140
00:08:53,890 --> 00:08:54,750
So pretty.

141
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,580
Look sweeter.

142
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:03,530
Ji-eun, you're doing so good.

143
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:05,530
Smile sweeter.

144
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:11,510
[The couple livestream begins]

145
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:16,060
Are you ready?

146
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:19,390
It'll be your couple livestream next.

147
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:23,830
The most classic scene
the fans want to watch.

148
00:09:27,460 --> 00:09:29,410
First, how you sit.

149
00:09:30,290 --> 00:09:32,830
Ji-eun will sit on Yebin-unnie's legs.

150
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:40,640
Second, you have to
put lipstick for each other.

151
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:43,490
Apply the 707 lipstick for each other

152
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:46,370
slowly and gently.

153
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:50,910
Third, to conclude things,

154
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:55,120
look into each other's eyes for 5 seconds
after applying the lipstick.

155
00:09:55,930 --> 00:09:57,360
You must look sincere

156
00:09:58,230 --> 00:09:59,770
and not look away.

157
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:02,040
Fourth,

158
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:04,490
it's a one-take, so there are no redos.

159
00:10:06,270 --> 00:10:07,520
Listen carefully.

160
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:09,780
We can't screw up this shoot again.

161
00:10:10,410 --> 00:10:12,860
Song Minah will film
and liven up the atmosphere.

162
00:10:12,860 --> 00:10:14,280
Just stick to the script.

163
00:10:15,050 --> 00:10:17,350
Then we'll definitely get many views.

164
00:10:18,450 --> 00:10:19,600
Yes, Mr. Lee.

165
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,260
I can't do this.

166
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,490
My legs hurt.

167
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:30,480
Your legs hurt?

168
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,390
Yebin.

169
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:34,650
Think carefully.

170
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:36,910
It's stated in the contract.

171
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,600
You have to pay 500 million won
for breach of contract.

172
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,430
Well, I'm sure you don't mind,

173
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,120
but Ji-eun's grandmother

174
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,320
has medical bills to pay next week.

175
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:48,180
The agency will no longer
financially support her.

176
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:50,230
And you'll be

177
00:10:51,850 --> 00:10:53,010
the cause of it.

178
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:56,370
Can you take the responsibility?

179
00:10:58,590 --> 00:10:59,810
Do it right.

180
00:11:06,310 --> 00:11:07,280
Unnie.

181
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,470
Don't worry.

182
00:11:09,570 --> 00:11:11,280
I'll stick to the script.

183
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:48,510
Good.

184
00:11:48,830 --> 00:11:49,970
In this posture,

185
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:52,050
Yebin-unnie,

186
00:11:52,050 --> 00:11:54,050
