227
00:19:55,670 --> 00:19:58,200
From today's lunch,
make changes to your diet.

228
00:19:58,200 --> 00:20:01,720
Add fruit. Dinner will be a salad
instead of a protein shake.

229
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:03,310
Really?

230
00:20:06,670 --> 00:20:07,930
Don't get too excited.

231
00:20:08,380 --> 00:20:11,380
It's just switching
from hell mode to difficult mode.

232
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:13,330
Yes, thank you, unnie.

233
00:20:14,390 --> 00:20:15,570
Warm up now.

234
00:20:17,340 --> 00:20:18,900
10 minutes of planks.

235
00:20:18,900 --> 00:20:21,120
20 sets of sit-ups.

236
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:22,670
10 minutes of stretching.

237
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:26,020
We'll practice the new choreography after.

238
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:27,990
Yes.

239
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,800
Don't resent me too much.

240
00:20:42,620 --> 00:20:45,860
Mr. Lee used to be a million times
stricter than this.

241
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:49,120
But thanks to him,

242
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:51,120
I'm where I am now.

